{"tid":364711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登音樂台] (求人整MV) 欣宜流行","createTime":"2017-08-18T15:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T15:34:07.000Z","uid":86038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"366e991ee97276832e4b1f58840cff61dbda23e6","tid":364711,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T15:30:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>欣宜流行</strong></span></span><br />\n原唱:古天樂 作詞：林夕&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 作曲：伍樂城<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">美極時尚 懇請欣賞<br />\n但你在吃肉 或是幻象<br />\n扮作道德樣 打卡得獎<br />\n肥胖仍是正常<br />\n<br />\n你以為 人人沉迷<br />\n你美麗 肉食拒絕 太虛偽<br />\n枱枱也橫行無忌 羊牛豬炸雞<br />\n欣宜流行 肥婆豬油淋淋<br />\n她肥騰騰 骨架會愈重愈近<br />\n終極肥人 猶如身型横行<br />\n癡肥形神 只不過是平權放任<br />\n<br />\n我是微胖 少許水腫<br />\n但我沒氣力 怎做運動<br />\n自信磅一磅 千斤誇張<br />\n肥胖其實正常<br />\n<br />\n你以為 肥婆迷人<br />\n裡美麗 但是發現 你虛偽<br />\n時常裡猴擒人地 肥婆春叫仔<br />\n欣宜橫行 肥婆光環流行<br />\n三層肥人 請不要愈坐愈近<br />\n今期流行 流行欣宜迷人<br />\n低頭無神 誇獎你是索命女神<br />\n<br />\n你以為 人人沉迷<br />\n你上圍 成層老泥 刮出嚟<br />\n肥人要橫行無忌 平權將炸毀<br />\n今期橫行 就像欣宜流行<br />\n風華凡塵 絲打要自信驟近<br />\n今期流行 流行癡肥岩神<br />\n改詞無仁 但是沒有像你害人</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝 <strong>口德分累積ing</strong> 巴打幫手編改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌唱人:<br />\n<strong>自由自在</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://clyp.it/jj121qom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fclyp.it%2Fjj121qom&d=On4r%2BQyPtzvYDtOv2KsQZ8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=e6bbf208\" target=\"_blank\">https://clyp.it/jj121qom</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求各位厲害既巴絲打幫手整MV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08ab81ed9250a354f319a3fa8ece07c31a175d1","tid":364711,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T15:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />